divs: Sighting Detailscoming out of the quickmart around 1:15am iwas getting in my vehicle when i looked up and noticed this bright green sphere like object falling to earth at high speed and at a angle not accustomed to a airplane landing. what struck me about this object was its sphere shape and green color and size of this object as it fell . i thought meteoir but htis size was huge and its glow and sphere shape. i'm sure i'm not the only one who seen this cause there was a highway next to me which was more elevated. i went to search remote area but with no success.
